---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../styles/page.css";
---

<Layout>

<section class="page">

<div class="container">


<div class="page-intro">

<span class="page-eyebrow">
Legal
</span>


<h1 class="page-title">
Cookie Policy
</h1>


<p class="page-description">

Learn how MonkeyReach uses cookies and similar technologies to improve website functionality, analytics, and user experience.

</p>


</div>



<div class="page-content">


<section class="page-card">

<h2>
1. What Are Cookies?
</h2>


<p>
Cookies are small text files stored on your device when you visit a website. They allow websites to function properly, remember preferences, and provide website owners with analytics and usage insights.
</p>


<p>
Similar technologies such as pixels, web beacons, local storage, and session storage may also be used.
</p>


</section>



<section class="page-card">

<h2>
2. Types of Cookies We Use
</h2>


<h3>
2.1 Strictly Necessary Cookies
</h3>


<p>
These cookies are essential for the operation and security of our website. Since Astro does not use WordPress sessions, we only use cookies required by installed services and functionality.
</p>


<ul>

<li>
Website security and essential functionality
</li>

<li>
Remembering privacy preferences
</li>

<li>
Maintaining required user settings
</li>

</ul>



<h3>
2.2 Analytics Cookies
</h3>


<p>
Analytics cookies help us understand visitor behaviour, website performance, and user interaction so we can improve our services.
</p>


<ul>

<li>
Google Analytics (if enabled)</li>

<li>
Traffic measurement</li>

<li>
Performance analysis</li>

</ul>



<h3>
2.3 Marketing Cookies
</h3>


<p>
Marketing cookies may be used to measure advertising performance and understand campaign effectiveness.
</p>


<ul>

<li>
Google Ads conversion tracking</li>

<li>
Campaign attribution</li>

<li>
Advertising measurement</li>

</ul>



</section>




<section class="page-card">

<h2>
3. Third-Party Services
</h2>


<p>
MonkeyReach may use trusted third-party platforms that may place cookies or collect usage information.
</p>


<ul>

<li>
Google Analytics — Website analytics
</li>

<li>
Google Ads — Advertising measurement
</li>

<li>
Make.com — Automation workflows
</li>

</ul>


</section>




<section class="page-section">

<h2>
4. Cookie Consent
</h2>


<p>
Where required, visitors may manage cookie preferences through our cookie consent controls. You can accept, reject, or modify your preferences at any time.
</p>


</section>




<section class="page-section">

<h2>
5. Managing Cookies
</h2>


<p>
You can control cookies through your browser settings. Most browsers allow you to block, delete, or receive warnings before cookies are stored.
</p>


<ul>

<li>
Google Chrome
</li>

<li>
Mozilla Firefox
</li>

<li>
Apple Safari
</li>

<li>
Microsoft Edge
</li>

</ul>


</section>




<section class="page-section">

<h2>
6. Changes To This Policy
</h2>


<p>
We may update this Cookie Policy periodically to reflect changes in technology, regulations, or business practices. Updates will be posted on this page with a revised date.
</p>


</section>




<section class="page-card">

<h2>
7. Contact Us
</h2>


<p>
If you have questions about this Cookie Policy, contact MonkeyReach Media:
</p>


<p>

